[normal](iii)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]      Furthermore water vapour is an 
[normal]important greenhouse g
[normal]as.  The amount 
[normal]of water vapour, mainly found in the lowest kilometer of the atmosphere 
[normal]very much depends
[normal] on lower atmosphere temperatures and dynamical processes.  This is a large contributor to global greenhouse warming that should be 
[normal]more carefully 
[normal]evaluated.  
