[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Has AR5 sufficiently explained the reasons behind the widely reported hiatus in the global sur[bold]face temperature record?[bold] [bold]Does the AR5 address the reliability of climate models?  Has AR5 sufficiently explained the reasons behind the widely reported hiatus in the global surface temperature record?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]        
[normal]“[bold]Climate is now [bold]a weather scale process [bold]problem”.[bold] [bold]&#xa0;
[normal](iv)
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]    ”
[normal]Climate is now a weather scale 
[normal]process problem`` and unless
[normal] 
[normal]these weather processes are understood
[normal] and 
[normal]included, then 
[normal]predictions are 
[normal]very 
[normal]likely to 
[normal]be 
